FT  08 MAY 91 / Ulster shops grow
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
NORTHERN IRELAND retailers are riding out the recession better than their
counterparts in other UK regions, a report claimed yesterday.
The report, Retail Property Belfast, published by the Northern Ireland
