FT  08 MAY 91 / UK Company News: Exports boost Toye to Pounds 0.72m
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Increased exports helped boost pre-tax profits at Toye, the civil and
military regalia manufacturer, from Pounds 690,493 to Pounds 720,915 for the
year to end-December.
Turnover was ahead 12 per cent from Pounds 11.03m to Pounds 12.39m. The
increase included a rise of 37 per cent in direct exports, valued at Pounds
1.73m.
