Conservative                   245     1,135    -890
Labour                         672       208    +490
Liberal Democrats              750       230    +520
Plaid Cymru                     36        14     +22
Green                            9         2      +7
Independent                    168       284    -116
Other                           59        92     -33
 -----------------------------------------------------------
